items.sentence: Tom wasn't sitting at his desk when I entered his office.
Tom kept stepping on Mary's feet while they were dancing.
The only time I ever did that was when I did it with you.
I didn't realize that what you were doing was helping me.
Tom was the only person at the party that Mary talked to.
If you have any questions, please feel fee to contact us.
It took me three hours of scrubbing to clean the skillet.
We had to delay our departure because of the bad weather.
It's better to light a candle than to curse the darkness.
I refuse to get in the car if Tom is going to be driving.
